ult-0000011251</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=2| 1991\n| ''[[Lips Together, Teeth Apart]]''\n| Sam Truman\n| New York City Center, Off-Broadway\n|<ref>http://iobdb.com/Search?searchText=lips+together%2C+teeth+apart&searchDomain=Any</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[On Borrowed Time]]''\n|  Mr. Brink\n| [[Circle in the Square Theatre]], Broadway\n|<ref>http://www.playbill.com/production/on-borrowed-time-circle-in-the-square-theatre-vault-0000003245</ref>\n|-\n| 1992\n| ''[[Guys and Dolls]]''\n| Nathan Detroit\n| [[Martin Beck Theatre]], Broadway\n| <ref>http://www.playbill.com/production/guys-and-dolls-martin-beck-theatre-vault-0000008217</ref>\n|-\n| 1993\n| ''[[Laughter on the 23rd Floor]]''\n| Max Prince\n| [[Richard Rogers Theatre]], Broadway\n|<ref>http://www.playbill.com/production/laughter-on-the-23rd-floor-richard-rodgers-theatre-vault-0000003079</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=2| 1994\n| rowspan=2| ''[[Love! Valour! Compassion!]]''\n| rowspan=2| Buzz Hauser\n| New York City Center, Off-Broadway\n|<ref>http://iobdb.com/Production/745</ref>\n|-\n| [[Walter Kerr Theatre]], Broadway\n|<ref>http://www.playbill.com/production/love-valour-compassion-walter-kerr-theatre-vault-0000010050</ref>\n|-\n| 1996\n| ''[[A Funny Thing Happened on the Way to the Forum]]''\n| Pseudolus\n| [[St. James Theatre]], Broadway\n|<ref>http://www.playbill.com/production/a-funny-thing-happened-on-the-way-to-the-forum-st-james-theatre-vault-0000004175</ref>\n|-\n| 1998\n| ''Mizlansky/Zilinsky or \"Schmucks\"''\n| Davis Mizlansky\n| New York City Center, Off-Broadway\n|<ref>http://iobdb.com/Search?searchText=Mizlansky%2FZilinsky+or+%22Schmucks&searchDomain=Any</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=2| 1999\n| ''[[Do Re Mi (musical)|Do Re Mi]]''\n| Hubert Cram\n| New York City Center, Concert\n|<ref>https://www.nytimes.com/section/theater?byline=By%2520BEN%2520BRANTLEY&html_title=&id=1077011429770&pdate=19990508&tols_title=DO%2520RE%2520MI%2520(PLAY)</ref>\n|-\n| ''[[Bounce (musical)|Wise Guys]]''\n| Addison Mizner\n| New York Workshop\n|<ref>ht