est Cast|National Board of Review Award, Best Acting by an Ensemble]]\n|{{WON}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" |2005\n| rowspan=\"3\" |''[[The Lion King 1\u00bd]]''\n|[[DVD Exclusive Awards|DVD Exclusive Award, Best Original Song - for \"Hakuna Matata\"]]\n|{{Nominated}}\n|-\n|[[DVD Exclusive Awards|DVD Exclusive Award, Best Original Song - \"That's All I Need\"]]\n|{{Nominated}}\n|-\n|[[DVD Exclusive Awards|DVD Exclusive Award, Best Animated Character Performance]]\n|{{WON}}\n|-\n|2006\n|''[[The Producers (2005 film)|The Producers]]''\n|AARP Movies for Grownups Award, Best Lead Actor\n|{{Nominated}}\n|}\n\n=== Television Awards ===\n'''Primetime Emmy Award'''\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Year\n!Title\n!Accolade\n!Results\n|-\n|1995\n|''[[Frasier]]: Fool Me Once, Shame on You. Fool Me Twice...''\n|[[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Guest Actor in a Comedy Series|Outstanding Guest Actor in a Comedy Series]]\n|{{Nominated}}\n|-\n|1998\n|''[[Mad About You]]: Good Old Reliable Nathan''\n|[[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Guest Actor in a Comedy Series|Outstanding Guest Actor in a Comedy Series]]\n|{{Nominated}}\n|-\n|2011\n|''[[Modern Family]]''\n|[[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Guest Actor in a Comedy Series|Outstanding Guest Actor in a Comedy Series]]\n|{{Nominated}}\n|-\n|2013\n|''[[The Good Wife]]''\n|[[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Guest Actor in a Drama Series|Outstanding Guest Actor in a Drama Series]]\n|{{Nominated}}\n|-\n|2013\n|''[[Modern Family]]: A Slight at the Opera''\n|[[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Guest Actor in a Comedy Series|Outstanding Guest Actor in a Comedy Series]]\n|{{Nominated}}\n|-\n|2014\n|''[[Modern Family]]''\n|[[Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Guest Actor in a Comedy Series|Outstanding Guest Actor in a Comedy Series]]\n|{{Nominated}}\n|}\n\n'''Daytime Emmy Awards'''\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Year\n!Title\n!Accolade\n!Results\n|-\n|1996\n|''[[Timon & Pumbaa (TV series)|Timon & Pumbaa]]''\n|[[Daytime Emmy Award for Outstanding Performer in an Animated Program|Outstanding Performer in an Animated Program]]\n|{{won}}\n|-\n|2000\n|''[[George and Martha]]''\n|[[Daytime Emmy Award for Outstanding Performer in an Animated Program|Outstanding Performer in an Animated Program]]\n|{{Nominated}}\n|-\n|2001\n|''[[Teacher's Pet (TV series)|Teacher's Pet]]''\n|[[Daytime Emmy Award for Outstanding Performer in an Animated Program|Outstanding Performer in an Animated Program]]\n|{{WON}}\n|}\n\n=== Theater accolades ===\n'''Tony Awards'''\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Year\n!Title\n!Accolade\n!Results\n|-\n|1992\n|''[[Guys and Dolls (musical)|Guys and Dolls]]''\n|[[Tony Award for Best Actor in a Musical|Best Actor in a Musical]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|1996\n|''[[A Funny Thing Happened on the Way to the Forum]]''\n|[[Tony Award for Best Actor in a Musical|Best Actor in a Musical]]\n|{{win}}\n|-\n|2001 \n|''[[The Producers (musical)|The Producers]]''\n|[[Tony Award for Best Actor in a Musical|Best Actor in a Musical]]\n|{{win}}\n|-\n|2013\n|''[[The Nance]]''\n|[[Tony Award for Best Actor in a Play|Best Actor in a Play]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|2017\n|''[[The Front Page]]''\n|[[Tony Award for Best Featured Actor in a Play|Best Featured Actor in a Play]]\n|{{nom}}\n|-\n|2018\n|''[[Angels in America]]''\n|[[Tony Award for Best Featured Actor in a Play|Best Featured Actor in a Play]]\n|{{win}}\n|}\n\n'''Drama Desk Awards'''\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Year\n!Title\n!Accolade\n!Results\n|-\n|1983\n|''[[Present Laughter]]''\n|[[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Featured Actor in a Play|Featured Actor in a Play]]\n|{{Nominated}}\n|-\n|1990\n|''[[The Lisbon Traviata]]''\n|[[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Actor in a Play|Actor in a Play]]\n|{{WON}}\n|-\n|1992\n|''[[Guys and Dolls]]''\n|[[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Actor in a Musical|Actor in a Musical]]\n|{{WON}}\n|-\n|1995\n|''[[Love! Valour! Compassion!]]''\n|[[Drama Desk Award for Outstanding Featured Actor in a Play|Featured Actor in a Play]]\n|{{WON